model.search

Class SearchFlights

  • java.lang.Object
    • model.search.SearchFlights

  • public class SearchFlights
extends java.lang.Object
    This class search both of one-way trip and round-way trip that satisfy customer's requirement. Class member attributes are the same as defined by the view.
